<!-- Shared Behavior -->
<section>
  <h2>Shared Behavior</h2>

  <h3>Progressive Enhancement</h3>
  <p>All retro text effects are CSS-only and need no JavaScript. Text is fully readable if the pack CSS is not loaded.</p>

  <h3>Reduced Motion</h3>
  <p>All animated effects respect <code>prefers-reduced-motion: reduce</code> and <code>:root[data-motion-reduced]</code>. Animations are disabled; static styling (shadows, outlines) remains.</p>

  <h3>Print</h3>
  <p>Animations, filters, and text-shadows are stripped in print media. Text renders in its default color.</p>

  <h3>CSS Layer</h3>
  <p>All rules are scoped to <code>@layer bundle-effects</code>.</p>
</section>

